302
00:17:37,341 --> 00:17:38,592
Também não sabe dela?

303
00:17:38,594 --> 00:17:40,412
Beth? Beth,
pode pegar os contatos

304
00:17:40,414 --> 00:17:42,419
do Sr. Mailer? Obrigado.

305
00:17:45,815 --> 00:17:48,148
Marcy, é MacLaren.

306
00:17:49,618 --> 00:17:51,151
Carly?

307
00:17:53,662 --> 00:17:54,894
Trevor? Philip?

308
00:17:56,491 --> 00:17:57,833
Droga.

309
00:18:05,166 --> 00:18:07,366
Agora expire.

310
00:18:08,770 --> 00:18:11,225
Sinta o silêncio
entre as respirações.

311
