492
00:27:38,833 --> 00:27:41,644
Era garoto e pensei

493
00:27:42,238 --> 00:27:44,647
"É tão injusto."

494
00:27:47,752 --> 00:27:49,619
Philip, fique calado.

495
00:27:49,621 --> 00:27:51,887
Não sei se consigo.

496
00:27:52,923 --> 00:27:54,189
Philip...

497
00:27:54,191 --> 00:27:55,424
Philip!

498
00:27:55,426 --> 00:27:56,591
Vou tentar.

499
00:27:56,593 --> 00:27:57,859
Philip. Philip?

