501
00:28:00,196 --> 00:28:01,195
Philip!

502
00:28:01,197 --> 00:28:04,031
Vou tentar. Vou tentar...

503
00:28:04,033 --> 00:28:05,833
<i>Philip?</i>

504
00:28:05,835 --> 00:28:06,901
<i>Philip!</i>

505
00:28:14,042 --> 00:28:15,319
Philip?

506
00:28:19,882 --> 00:28:21,600
Philip?

507
00:28:45,473 --> 00:28:47,639
Onde vocês estão?

508
00:28:52,479 --> 00:28:55,146
