510
00:28:56,583 --> 00:28:58,717
<i>"...Planeja falhar."</i>

511
00:28:58,719 --> 00:29:00,218
<i>"Planejar é essencial."</i>

512
00:29:00,742 --> 00:29:04,488
<i>"Se falhar em planejar,
