513
00:29:04,490 --> 00:29:07,090
Benjamin Franklin.

514
00:29:07,768 --> 00:29:08,499
Plano principal?

515
00:29:10,029 --> 00:29:11,929
"Nenhum plano de batalha..."

516
00:29:11,931 --> 00:29:13,197
<i>Plano de batalha...</i>

517
00:29:13,199 --> 00:29:15,132
